      Our goal is to provide our customers with a seamless offering of products that spans the web, the real world, and the different mobile mediumsâ€”allowing them to go mobile, use open standards, and reach more people. 
    </quote>" On this site, they provide javascript outlines for congressional districts.
  </p>
  
  <h2>Other Mash-it Partners</h2>
  <p>
    Bill Track currently uses google's mapping API extensively. I am hoping the site will expand to get twitter tweets, youtube videos and many other social web 2.0 things. As needs arise, which surely it will if the site prospers, more connections will be made with applications and APIs focused on shining the light of truth on government.
